<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DINKSIRA - Clothing Collection</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: #2c3824;
            color: #e8dfca;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 40px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 0 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #9e8968;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #f2e6cc;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #cbad72;
            margin-top: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #dbba7c;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            color: #efcd9a;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        .product-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 30px;
            margin: 50px 0;
        }
        .product-card {
            background: #2a3a24;
            border: 1px solid #7a6a4a;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .product-card:hover {
            border-color: #c9a96e;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .product-card img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            filter: sepia(0.15);
        }
        .product-card h3 {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin: 15px 0 5px;
            color: #f2e6cc;
        }
        .product-card p {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #c7bc98;
        }
        .price {
            color: #dbba7c;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #7a6a4a;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #94845c;
        }
        @media (max-width: 860px) {
            .product-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>CLOTHING</h1>
            <p>Timeless silhouettes — handcrafted in Ethiopia</p>
            <a href="index.html" class="back-link">← BACK TO HOME</a>
        </div>
        <div class="product-grid">
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="Screenshot%202026-05-01%20at%2012.51.41.png" alt="Wool Coat">
                <h3>Asymmetric Wool Coat</h3>
                <p>Hand-finished tailoring</p>
                <div class="price">$489</div>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="Screenshot%202026-05-01%20at%2012.47.07.png" alt="Linen Shirt">
                <h3>Folded Seam Shirt</h3>
                <p>Organic linen</p>
                <div class="price">$189</div>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="Screenshot%202026-05-01%20at%2012.51.41.png" alt="Trousers">
                <h3>Draped Trousers</h3>
                <p>Raw edge finish</p>
                <div class="price">$279</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>© 2025 DINKSIRA — Handmade by Ethiopians</footer>
</body>
</html>
